snippet.title: Frontline Fury: Trenches, Mud & Blood - Steam Next Fest Trailer - New Top Down Shooter 2025
snippet.description:
Play the Demo on:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3066070/Frontline_Fury__Trenches_Mud__Blood/

Want to know more? Join our Discord:
https://discord.gg/QvQSH7YT

Enter the brutal battlefields of World War II in this grim, blood-soaked top-down shooter. Fight your way through relentless enemies with brutal gunplay, gritty visuals, and intense, unforgiving combat. Every bullet counts as you move through the trenches, leaving a trail of destruction and gore.
